description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool, using the InfluxDB exporter

targets.query: SELECT count("value"), min("value"), median("value"), max("value"), mean("value"), percentile("value", 90), percentile("value", 95), percentile("value", 99) FROM "http_req_duration" WHERE  $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT  min("value"), median("value"), max("value"), mean("value"), percentile("value", 90), percentile("value", 95), percentile("value", 99) FROM "group_duration" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY "group"

SELECT count("value") FROM "http_reqs" WHERE ("status" = '400' OR "status" = '401' OR "status" = '403' OR "status" = '404' OR "status" = '405' OR "status" = '406' OR "status" = '407' OR "status" = '408' OR "status" = '409' OR "status" = '410') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT count("value") FROM "http_reqs" WHERE ("status" = '500' OR "status" = '501' OR "status" = '502' OR "status" = '503' OR "status" = '504' OR "status" = '505') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT min("value") FROM $Measurement WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0
SELECT max("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT percentile("value", 95) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT percentile("value", 90) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT min("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

title: k6 General dashboard
